
# # # Expand EXT4:
$ sudo resize2fs /dev/sda2

Shrink EXT4 (Offline):
$ sudo resize2fs -M /dev/sda1

# # # Resize NTFS:
$ sudo ntfsfix -d -b /dev/sda1

# Check Space Left:
$ sudo ntfsresize --info /dev/sdb3 | grep Space | awk {'print $5'}

# Set new space:
$ sudo ntfsresize --size 40G /dev/sda1 -f
